arlut.csd.ganymede.client
Class FieldOptionRow

java.lang.Object
  arlut.csd.ganymede.client.FieldOptionRow

 class FieldOptionRow
extends java.lang.Object

An instance of this class is attached to each node in the JTree. The hooks in this class allow us to refer to the DBObjectBase / DBObjectBaseField that the corresponding node in the tree represents. It also holds the value of the options for each node in the tree.
